This paper deals with the problem of obstacle avoidance and navigation for ground robots, which is a core topic in the field of robotics. The paper focuses on formal verification of controllers for ensuring safety of the robot, which is a key aspect of robotics research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
